Note:
C# Lexer - Tokenization for C# programming language

This file provides complete tokenization for C# source code.
Handles all C# keywords, operators, literals, comments, and syntax elements.

Features:
- Complete C# keyword recognition (77 keywords)
- All C# operators and delimiters (including ??, ?., ?:, =>)
- Integer literals (decimal, hex, binary with digit separators)
- Floating-point literals (with f, d, m suffixes)
- String literals (regular, verbatim @"", interpolated $"")
- Character literals with escape sequences
- Comments (line and block, including XML documentation ///)
- Identifiers with Unicode support

Dependencies:
- compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa
:End Note

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout

